    <sect1>
        <title>Guest Speaker side</title>
        <para>When you are on the plus.google.com page, you will see a notice in the upper right of
            the page indicating that there is a new conversation. I was finally able to capture this
            by using a 2nd computer and inviting myself to join.</para>
        <figure>
            <title>New conversation</title>
            <mediaobject>
                <imageobject>
                    <imagedata fileref="New%20conversation.png" contentdepth="100%" scalefit="1"
                        width="100%"/>
                </imageobject>
            </mediaobject>
        </figure>
        <para>Clicking on that message will open up another dialog where to can click the video icon
            to join the Hangout.</para>
        <figure>
            <title>Click to join</title>
            <mediaobject>
                <imageobject>
                    <imagedata fileref="Click%20to%20join.png" contentdepth="100%" scalefit="1"
                        width="100%"/>
                </imageobject>
            </mediaobject>
        </figure>
    </sect1>
